version_description:
- 2017 Toyota AFL Premiership Season rollover
- Enhanced designs for tablets
- Bug fixes

-Easily identify your Captain in the player list
-Buy tickets from the Match Preview
-Accessibility improvements to Video, Ladder and Fixture pages
-Increased font size available in news articles for low vision users

Exciting new features include:
- Club EMOJI keyboards
- Top player snapshots
- News and videos are now more prominent in menus
- Voiceover users can now recognise card titles
- Minor bug fixes

- Club themed Face Paint masks
- Extra time for the 2017 Finals Series
- minor bug fixes

We have made some changes to the way you login to the Collingwood app. Some users may be presented with the login screen and asked to create a Collingwood account - or you can login with your Collingwood membership account to access your digital membership card as well as other exclusive content from the club. This of course can be skipped if you choose not to.
Fixed an issue where some users where experiencing crashing of the app.
Fixed an issue where no content was displaying on first launch for some users
